                                 <source srcset="assets/images/photos/Innovation_list.png" type="image/png"> 
                                <img src="assets/images/photos/Innovation_list.png" alt="List page example desktop" class="figure-img img-fluid w-100">
                                </picture>
                    </div>   
                    
                    <div class="col-lg-12 mb-0 mb-lg-3 row justify-content-center">
                        <figure class="figure mb-0" data-aos="fade-in">
                            <picture>
                                 <source srcset="assets/images/photos/styleguide.png" type="image/webp">
                                 <source srcset="assets/images/photos/styleguide.png" type="image/png"> 
                                <img src="assets/images/photos/styleguide.png" alt="Style guide examples" class="figure-img img-fluid w-100 ">
                            </picture>
                        </div>
                    
                    <div class="col-lg-8 mb-3 mb-lg-2"> 
                    <blockquote class="bqspecial bqstext p-4 text-left font-weight-normal my-3 font-size-5" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="500"><h2>Result</h2>Demo to leadership and account team went smoothly. By deploying this tool, we increased customer’s visibility into DXC’s innovations from the results of the tracking process. We enable customers to measure DXC’s innovation capability with these metrices, one vehicle being the NPS. We increased DXC’s NPS especially in the area of innovation which enables customers to recommend DXC based on the ability to generate new ideas and develop creative ways to resolving business problems.</blockquote>
                     </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
